  <編章節>   Chapter I: General Provisions</編章節>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[These standards are set forth in accordance with the second paragraph of Article 10 of Act Governing Food Safety and Sanitation.
]]></條文內容>
