  <條文>
    <條號>Article 19</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Food factories that fail to meet the basic facility, production equipment or inspection equipment requirements provided in Article 8 to Article 18 in the Standards are required to submit a statement explaining the reason(s) and provide supporting documents.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <編章節>   Chapter IV. Supplementary Provisions</編章節>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 20</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[These standards shall be implemented from the date of promulgation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
